        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>green tomato chutney</strong>,<strong> cider vinegar</strong> and <strong>wholegrain mustard</strong> to a small bowl</p> <p>Add 2 tbsp\u00a0<span class=\"text-danger\">[4\u00a0tbsp]</span>\u00a0<strong>olive oil </strong>and season with a pinch\u00a0of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper\u00a0</strong></p> <p>Give everything a good mix up \u2013 this is your<strong> chutney dressing</strong>\u00a0</p>",
